16
00:01:38,041 --> 00:01:39,158
Yeah, yeah.

17
00:01:39,222 --> 00:01:40,521
Arianne.

18
00:01:40,934 --> 00:01:41,923
Uh, Jered.

19
00:01:41,911 --> 00:01:44,111
So... Jered.

20
00:01:44,593 --> 00:01:46,445
