I'll tell you what, love.

44
00:03:11,180 --> 00:03:13,518
Why don't we give you some new clothes?

45
00:03:15,532 --> 00:03:17,066
I'm really not sure about this.

46
00:03:33,555 --> 00:03:34,740
You'll be fine.

47
00:03:35,404 --> 00:03:38,561
